{"tid":550014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★唔捱得！病情沒好轉 20後廢老持刀往診所找晦氣被捕！","createTime":"2018-02-04T09:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T09:46:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e32d7d0865ea356424e86fc0ae7d4ccb9313b4eb","tid":550014,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:48:42.000Z","msg":"荃灣一名患濕疹老翁不滿病情沒好轉，帶刀上中醫診所找晦氣。姓黃(91歲)老翁，本身患有濕疹，並需手持拐杖，今晨9時許，他到南豐中心一間中醫診所，向職員表示不滿病情沒有好轉，要求見為其診症的中醫師，但職員指中醫師不在，雙方一度理論，期間有人突然情緒激動，向職員表示自己身懷一柄利刀，一名25歲女職員聞言大驚報警。警員到場調查，在老翁所攜帶的環保袋內發現一柄一呎長生果刀，調查後，將黃拘捕帶署，案件暫列刑事恐嚇，交荃灣警區刑事調查隊跟進。被捕時老翁疑似濕疹發作，禁不住一邊離開一邊抓癢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180204/bkn-20180204102058391-0204_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180204%2Fbkn-20180204102058391-0204_00822_001.html&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3b9ecfff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180204/bkn-20180204102058391-0204_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5ea54bffa7ad68f0de6ce5da252d46f743241ec7","tid":550014,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180204/photo/bkn-20180204102058391-0204_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180204172302\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180204%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180204102058391-0204_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180204172302&h=62456462&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"585eaf2ab544200fb285cea88c72218c839c5651","tid":550014,"uid":62815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:51:23.000Z","msg":"九十歲殺人放火真係無撚敵<br />\n你判我終生咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2347e691c6380a5a1df33b51378c49f13a82a2","tid":550014,"uid":98915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"585eaf2ab544200fb285cea88c72218c839c5651","tid":550014,"uid":62815,"like":3,